snippet.title: BLOOD ORANGE: Definitive Edition Trailer
snippet.description:
​Surprise!! 'BLOOD ORANGE: Definitive Edition' doubles the exploration, reinvents the gameplay, and expands the story. Coming to STEAM, for FREE, on November 3.


Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2655840/Blood_Orange_Definitive_Edition/

Trailer Edited by Myles Ogilvie AKA DireTone
https://m27ogilvie.wixsite.com/portfolio
